description:
Club the Unclubbed.
Here we try to build a club in Berlin, we will use swarm intelligence, NFTs, and an avant-garde approach to create a DAO, that forget everything about how things were done in the past.
payDisclosure:
This is an experimental project, that comes after years and years of research on how to do things right. The complexity of this project lives in the application of Chaos Theory, Emergence and other mathematical and scientific theories (Spontaneous order). I will do my best, to make this project innovative and fun, but i can-t do it without you, so please, join our discord. https://discord.gg/SvUFTYEMDy
This project will also be the subject of my paper. Please, don-t risk money that you can-t afford to lose, we want to make people happy, not sad.
